1
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:39,950
[The Story of Xing Fu]

2
00:01:40,050 --> 00:01:42,950
[Episode 40]

3
00:01:44,239 --> 00:01:45,079
This way, please.

4
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:55,719
Here is Tongxian Hall.

5
00:01:55,799 --> 00:01:56,519
Thank you.

6
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:58,519
Here.

7
00:01:58,599 --> 00:01:59,719
Okay, let's do it.

8
00:02:03,159 --> 00:02:04,480
Try the specialty here.

9
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:05,840
Thank you.

10
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:06,840
Mr. Han.

11
00:02:07,159 --> 00:02:08,280
I'd like to give you a toast.

12
00:02:08,439 --> 00:02:09,239
Don't, sit.

13
00:02:09,239 --> 00:02:10,359
Let's sit down and drink.

14
00:02:10,439 --> 00:02:10,799
Okay.

15
00:02:19,639 --> 00:02:20,919
Please excuse me for a minute.

16
00:02:21,319 --> 00:02:21,960
Okay.

17
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:23,080
You guys eat.

18
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:24,080
Okay, let's eat.

19
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:28,879
Why are you here?

20
00:02:29,199 --> 00:02:30,960
Aren't you preparing the materials
at Wan Village?

21
00:02:32,199 --> 00:02:32,879
Mr. Han.

22
00:02:33,599 --> 00:02:35,840
There is illegal discharge
at the wastewater treatment plant.

23
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:43,240
Illegal discharge, you say?

24
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:44,719
Did they tell you themselves?

25
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:45,919
No.

26
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,520
I found out while going through the materials.

27
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:49,159
In the past three years,

28
00:02:49,159 --> 00:02:50,439
particularly this year,

29
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,639
the treatment plant's quantity

30
00:02:51,639 --> 00:02:53,479
and purchase frequency
of chemicals have obviously declined.

31
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:56,599
It's the same for the plant's operation cost.

32
00:02:56,759 --> 00:02:58,400
That too shows an obvious decline.

33
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:02,360
I've suspected it since long ago.

34
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:06,039
So Mr. Mo is indeed capable of such acts.

35
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:08,240
What should we do now, Mr. Han?

36
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:11,560
Did you come here because of this?

37
00:03:12,759 --> 00:03:14,080
What's so hard?

38
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,719
So long as the plaintiff
does not have the evidence,

39
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:18,120
it won't be much of a threat to us.

40
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:20,439
But...

41
00:03:20,719 --> 00:03:22,520
But they are discharging illegally.

42
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:24,319
So? What about it?

43
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:25,721
Alright, I'll remind Mr. Mo

44
00:03:25,721 --> 00:03:26,920
to redo the data

45
00:03:26,920 --> 00:03:27,920
as soon as possible.

46
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:29,800
If they find out, we'd have to yield.

47
00:03:30,040 --> 00:03:31,681
But what they're doing is illegal!

48
00:03:31,920 --> 00:03:33,520
Keep your voice down.

49
00:03:37,721 --> 00:03:39,040
What is with the fuss?

50
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:40,441
This isn't a big deal.

51
00:03:43,321 --> 00:03:43,800
You.

52
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:45,960
Just go back and get the materials ready.

53
00:03:46,441 --> 00:03:47,640
I heard that the people of Shuiwei Village

54
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:48,721
aren't exactly united.

55
00:03:49,321 --> 00:03:50,760
Get on your sister too.

56
00:03:50,881 --> 00:03:51,800
As long as she doesn't push it,

57
00:03:51,881 --> 00:03:53,760
the lawsuit probably won't proceed.

58
00:03:53,881 --> 00:03:54,681
But Mr. Han, they...

59
00:03:54,681 --> 00:03:55,281
Alright, enough.

60
00:03:55,561 --> 00:03:56,640
I have to get back to the clients.

61
00:03:56,681 --> 00:03:57,760
That is all.

62
00:03:58,401 --> 00:03:58,920
Wait.

63
00:03:59,040 --> 00:03:59,601
Off you go.

64
00:04:02,200 --> 00:04:04,001
Sorry about that, Mr. Wang. Let us continue.

65
00:04:24,071 --> 00:04:35,371
[Tongjun Restaurant]

66
00:04:35,396 --> 00:04:37,721
[Xingfu]

67
00:04:52,520 --> 00:04:53,121
Xingfu.

68
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:55,561
Are you back?

69
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:58,361
I'm on the way home.

70
00:04:58,840 --> 00:05:00,441
Tell Mom to wait for me to eat.

71
00:05:01,321 --> 00:05:02,760
I bought a lot of nice food.

72
00:05:06,001 --> 00:05:07,121
I'm back in the city.

73
00:05:07,840 --> 00:05:08,600
In the city?

74
00:05:10,121 --> 00:05:10,960
Why?

75
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:12,561
Did something happen?

76
00:05:12,881 --> 00:05:13,960
Did a case come up?

77
00:05:15,681 --> 00:05:16,160
Xingfu.

78
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:21,001
Why are you crying?

79
00:05:22,640 --> 00:05:24,160
What happened?

80
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,121
Did someone bully you?

81
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:26,080
Xingfu.

82
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:29,121
I wish to quit being a lawyer.

83
00:05:31,241 --> 00:05:32,840
I'm exhausted.

84
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:40,520
Xingfu.

85
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:43,441
Are you guys still going ahead

86
00:05:44,441 --> 00:05:45,720
with Shuiwei Village's case?

87
00:05:46,241 --> 00:05:47,481
Of course. Why shouldn't we?

88
00:05:47,840 --> 00:05:48,921
We've already signed the agreement.

89
00:05:49,681 --> 00:05:51,720
A total of 25 people
will file a class-action lawsuit.

90
00:05:52,441 --> 00:05:53,200
Xingyun.

91
00:05:54,361 --> 00:05:55,441
Did you find out something?

92
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:03,041
No.

93
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:05,041
Look,

94
00:06:05,041 --> 00:06:06,160
Xingfu, I have something else to do.

95
00:06:06,280 --> 00:06:07,600
I'm going to hang up.

96
00:06:11,001 --> 00:06:11,681
Okay.

97
00:06:26,760 --> 00:06:27,160
Hello?

98
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,280
Guan.

99
00:06:28,840 --> 00:06:31,041
My sister called me crying just now.

100
00:06:31,041 --> 00:06:32,400
She said she wanted to quit being a lawyer.

101
00:06:33,080 --> 00:06:34,361
From what I know of her,

102
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:36,001
there has to be something

103
00:06:36,001 --> 00:06:37,280
that is weighing heavily on her.

104
00:06:38,121 --> 00:06:38,801
Guan.

105
00:06:39,921 --> 00:06:40,760
I am positively sure

106
00:06:41,561 --> 00:06:43,361
that something is up
with the wastewater treatment plant.

107
00:07:16,481 --> 00:07:17,121
Xingyun.

108
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:17,881
Where are you?

109
00:07:19,121 --> 00:07:19,600
Xingfu.

110
00:07:19,801 --> 00:07:20,640
I've thought it through.

111
00:07:23,001 --> 00:07:24,241
I will continue to be a lawyer.

112
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:26,080
And I want to be a good one.

113
00:07:27,001 --> 00:07:27,801
I thought about it.

114
00:07:29,361 --> 00:07:31,600
We shouldn't run away from problems.

115
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:34,481
Only if we're brave

116
00:07:35,400 --> 00:07:37,640
can we become stronger.

117
00:07:40,321 --> 00:07:40,840
Xingyun.

118
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:41,921
I'm so happy

119
00:07:41,921 --> 00:07:43,200
that you've come around.

120
00:07:44,561 --> 00:07:45,241
Don't worry.

121
00:07:45,241 --> 00:07:47,080
No matter what you do, Mom and I will support you.

122
00:07:57,121 --> 00:07:58,881
You can do it!

123
00:08:08,080 --> 00:08:09,001
[Resignation Letter]
This is my resignation letter.

124
00:08:15,544 --> 00:08:17,021
[Staff ID]

125
00:08:19,760 --> 00:08:20,400
He.

126
00:08:21,561 --> 00:08:23,681
Are you going to leave

127
00:08:23,681 --> 00:08:24,681
before you achieve anything?

128
00:08:25,361 --> 00:08:27,160
Which law firm would want to hire you?

129
00:08:27,760 --> 00:08:28,840
Think about it.

130
00:08:28,840 --> 00:08:29,321
You

131
00:08:29,481 --> 00:08:30,801
went through a lot to get where you are today.

132
00:08:30,801 --> 00:08:32,200
How much have you sacrificed?

133
00:08:32,561 --> 00:08:34,121
How could you just give up like this?

134
00:08:34,801 --> 00:08:35,760
Is it worth it?

135
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:36,881
It's precisely because

136
00:08:36,881 --> 00:08:38,280
I do not want to make any more sacrifices.

137
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:42,281
And I did achieve something.

138
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:44,441
After all,

139
00:08:46,161 --> 00:08:47,080
when a person is full,

140
00:08:47,921 --> 00:08:49,080
they should look at more options.

141
00:08:50,161 --> 00:08:50,761
Mr. Han,

142
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:52,801
although I've never liked you,

143
00:08:53,761 --> 00:08:55,080
during my tenure in Yidao,

144
00:08:55,281 --> 00:08:56,561
I still want to thank you.

145
00:08:57,921 --> 00:08:59,521
It was this experience that made me realize

146
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:01,360
what it is that should be abandoned.

147
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:02,960
And what it is

148
00:09:03,161 --> 00:09:04,321
that I should hold onto.

149
00:09:18,880 --> 00:09:19,561
Yani.

150
00:09:19,880 --> 00:09:20,960
Stop being lovey-dovey.

151
00:09:21,041 --> 00:09:22,041
Come and eat.

152
00:09:22,041 --> 00:09:23,600
Okay, we're coming.

153
00:09:23,681 --> 00:09:24,321
I'm coming, Mom.

154
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:27,761
Mom, let me get the rice.

155
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:28,480
No, no.

156
00:09:28,681 --> 00:09:29,240
Sit down.

157
00:09:29,681 --> 00:09:30,561
I'll do it.

158
00:09:31,521 --> 00:09:32,401
Let's eat.

159
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:35,401
Packed all your things?

160
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:36,561
Almost done.

161
00:09:39,161 --> 00:09:39,641
Firstly,

162
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:40,480
put your chopsticks down.

163
00:09:41,681 --> 00:09:42,480
Here's a reminder.

164
00:09:43,161 --> 00:09:43,840
A serious one.

165
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,641
Regarding your honeymoon trip.

166
00:09:47,681 --> 00:09:48,840
No matter what the situation is,

167
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:49,441
make sure

168
00:09:50,521 --> 00:09:51,240
you two stay safe.

169
00:09:52,401 --> 00:09:52,921
Dad.

170
00:09:53,401 --> 00:09:55,120
You've said that a hundred times.

171
00:09:55,401 --> 00:09:56,000
Too little.

172
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:57,761
A hundred times isn't enough.

173
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:59,521
No matter how many times he says it,

174
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:00,480
it won't be enough.

175
00:10:00,761 --> 00:10:01,240
Am I right?

176
00:10:01,281 --> 00:10:01,921
Don't worry, Dad, Mom.

177
00:10:01,921 --> 00:10:03,840
We will make sure
to put safety first at all times.

178
00:10:04,641 --> 00:10:06,561
Here, have some beef.

179
00:10:06,561 --> 00:10:07,080
Thanks, Mom.

180
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:07,720
Hello, Guan.

181
00:10:08,521 --> 00:10:09,720
Dad, you should eat more.

182
00:10:09,880 --> 00:10:10,401
What's up?

183
00:10:10,641 --> 00:10:12,041
He doesn't eat beef.

184
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:13,080
He can't chew.

185
00:10:14,281 --> 00:10:15,480
Who said I don't eat meat?

186
00:10:15,761 --> 00:10:16,600
Mom said

187
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:18,240
you don't eat anything that walks on four legs.

188
00:10:18,681 --> 00:10:19,080
She's bullying me.

189
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:20,600
You can eat more.

190
00:10:20,921 --> 00:10:21,641
She won't give me meat.

191
00:10:21,880 --> 00:10:23,720
Young people should eat more.

192
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:28,000
Alright.

193
00:10:33,041 --> 00:10:34,521
I'll discuss it with Qingzhi first.

194
00:10:38,801 --> 00:10:39,840
What's the matter? Did something happen?

195
00:10:42,281 --> 00:10:43,360
Something big happened.

196
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:45,041
What is it?

197
00:10:46,641 --> 00:10:49,281
It's about the class action
filed by villagers of Shuiwei

198
00:10:49,281 --> 00:10:51,641
against Wanjia's illegal wastewater discharge.

199
00:10:54,681 --> 00:10:55,801
It's big news.

200
00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:57,120
I have to cover it.

201
00:10:59,441 --> 00:11:00,561
What about

202
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:03,600
we postpone

203
00:11:03,641 --> 00:11:04,681
the honeymoon trip?

204
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:08,521
Do you really have to go?

205
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:10,921
The earth doesn't revolve around you, right?

206
00:11:11,801 --> 00:11:12,441
Of course it does.

207
00:11:13,161 --> 00:11:14,521
How would the earth spin without Yani?

208
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:17,080
That's a huge burden on her.

209
00:11:17,880 --> 00:11:19,200
Work comes first.

210
00:11:19,561 --> 00:11:20,840
As for the honeymoon...

211
00:11:21,521 --> 00:11:22,761
Every day to you two

212
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:23,401
is like a honeymoon.

213
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:27,281
I think

214
00:11:27,360 --> 00:11:29,000
since we have plenty of time,

215
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:30,161
we can always go later.

216
00:11:31,120 --> 00:11:31,641
You can decide.

217
00:11:31,801 --> 00:11:32,321
I'll do as you say.

218
00:11:34,161 --> 00:11:36,120
Thanks, hubby. You're the best.

219
00:11:52,281 --> 00:11:53,041
Come in.

220
00:12:03,041 --> 00:12:03,720
Xingyun.

221
00:12:04,240 --> 00:12:04,921
Why are you here?

222
00:12:07,921 --> 00:12:09,200
I don't work for Yidao anymore.

223
00:12:10,521 --> 00:12:12,041
So should I congratulate you

224
00:12:12,880 --> 00:12:13,761
or comfort you?

225
00:12:15,641 --> 00:12:16,441
Congratulate me, I guess.

226
00:12:20,521 --> 00:12:21,960
What do you plan to do now?

227
00:12:24,480 --> 00:12:25,360
If I say

228
00:12:25,801 --> 00:12:26,960
that I wish to join Fangyuan

229
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:29,041
and work with you,

230
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:32,521
will you be willing to take me in?

231
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:43,960
Fangyuan Law Firm

232
00:12:44,641 --> 00:12:45,521
welcomes you.

233
00:12:46,561 --> 00:12:47,041
Congratulations.

234
00:12:59,761 --> 00:13:00,441
(Good day.)

235
00:13:00,801 --> 00:13:02,120
[Supreme People's Court]
(We are now standing)

236
00:13:02,281 --> 00:13:04,321
(in front of Fushui Town's courthouse.)

237
00:13:04,401 --> 00:13:05,921
Today's trial is the class action

238
00:13:05,921 --> 00:13:07,561
on the water pollution liability dispute

239
00:13:07,641 --> 00:13:09,561
filed by 25 villagers of Shuiwei Village

240
00:13:09,681 --> 00:13:11,120
against Wanjia Health Products Factory.

241
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:13,080
Wanjia Health Products Factory

242
00:13:13,161 --> 00:13:14,960
is a well-known township enterprise
in our province.

243
00:13:15,281 --> 00:13:17,041
A subsidiary company of Wanjia Group

244
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:18,801
started its operation in 2012.

245
00:13:34,621 --> 00:13:35,421
[Wanjia Health Products
Wastewater Treatment Plant]

246
00:14:17,310 --> 00:14:27,696
[Wan Village Wastewater Treatment Plant]

247
00:14:32,281 --> 00:14:34,200
Greetings, Your Honor, judges,

248
00:14:34,480 --> 00:14:35,681
and people's assessors.

249
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:38,161
As well as members of the public in attendance.

250
00:14:38,960 --> 00:14:40,960
I am an attorney from Fangyuan Law Firm,

251
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:41,720
Guan Tao.

252
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:42,641
[Plaintiff]

253
00:14:42,641 --> 00:14:44,161
I accepted the request from the plaintiffs,

254
00:14:44,321 --> 00:14:45,681
namely Li Yancheng, Guo Yaping, and others

255
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:47,360
to be their legal person

256
00:14:47,441 --> 00:14:49,200
in this litigation case.

257
00:14:49,360 --> 00:14:51,840
Before the court hearing,
we went over the evidence in detail

258
00:14:52,281 --> 00:14:53,561
and determined legal grounds.

259
00:14:53,880 --> 00:14:55,480
After today's court session,

260
00:14:55,561 --> 00:14:58,600
we have come to a conclusion about the case.

261
00:14:59,240 --> 00:15:00,600
Combining facts and law,

262
00:15:00,761 --> 00:15:02,441
these are our opinions.

263
00:15:04,641 --> 00:15:05,561
The plaintiffs believe

264
00:15:05,681 --> 00:15:07,681
that as the defendant is located
upstream of Fushui River

265
00:15:07,921 --> 00:15:10,720
and the wastewater treatment plant
is built beside Fushui River,

266
00:15:10,880 --> 00:15:13,761
it is the only wastewater treatment facility
in the area.

267
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:16,441
The plaintiffs are located
downstream of Fushui River.

268
00:15:16,600 --> 00:15:18,921
Their residences are near Fushui River.

269
00:15:19,840 --> 00:15:21,000
According to the evidence,

270
00:15:21,521 --> 00:15:23,921
the characteristics of the pollutants
discharged by the defendant

271
00:15:24,161 --> 00:15:26,600
are a match with the pollutants
found in the plaintiffs' well water.

272
00:15:26,960 --> 00:15:27,921
This shows

273
00:15:28,360 --> 00:15:31,521
that the defendant's wastewater management
has a causal relationship

274
00:15:31,641 --> 00:15:33,801
with the polluted well water.

275
00:15:36,080 --> 00:15:37,641
Wan Village organized for all villagers

276
00:15:37,641 --> 00:15:39,840
to undergo a blood lead test.

277
00:15:40,161 --> 00:15:41,840
The investigation results show

278
00:15:42,720 --> 00:15:43,321
that first,

279
00:15:43,401 --> 00:15:45,641
villagers who showed high levels of blood lead

280
00:15:45,720 --> 00:15:49,600
all drank well water or used it
over a long period of time;

281
00:15:50,120 --> 00:15:50,641
second,

282
00:15:50,641 --> 00:15:51,360
[Defendant]

283
00:15:51,360 --> 00:15:53,080
villagers who only drank well water

284
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:55,360
had blood lead levels that were higher

285
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:58,161
