I'm not sure either.

570
00:32:37,891 --> 00:32:38,781
Mr. Wan asked us to come.

571
00:32:38,781 --> 00:32:39,651
Let's just sit in.

572
00:32:57,381 --> 00:32:58,171
Today,

573
00:32:59,171 --> 00:33:01,021
I've invited everyone here personally

574
00:33:02,021 --> 00:33:02,891
as Wan Shantang.

575
00:33:05,021 --> 00:33:06,411
You've probably heard.

576
00:33:06,821 --> 00:33:08,341
I have officially tendered

577
00:33:08,341 --> 00:33:09,211
my resignation

578
00:33:09,341 --> 00:33:09,861
with

579
00:33:09,861 --> 00:33:10,731
the Wan Village committee

580
00:33:11,261 --> 00:33:12,341
and village party branch.

581
00:33:15,171 --> 00:33:15,861
Now,

582
00:33:16,581 --> 00:33:17,211
on behalf

583
00:33:17,781 --> 00:33:18,651
of myself

584
00:33:18,891 --> 00:33:20,021
and my son,

585
00:33:20,781 --> 00:33:21,821
Wan Chuanjia,

586
00:33:22,691 --> 00:33:24,491
I'd like to apologize to the villagers

587
00:33:25,691 --> 00:33:27,261
who have suffered due to

588
00:33:28,451 --> 00:33:29,101
the pollution incident.

589
00:33:33,651 --> 00:33:34,381
In addition,

590
00:33:35,021 --> 00:33:37,021
I have something else to announce.

591
00:33:42,411 --> 00:33:43,061
Chuanmei.

592
00:34:04,691 --> 00:34:05,651
Hello, everyone.

593
00:34:07,301 --> 00:34:08,301
I am Wan Chuanmei.

594
00:34:09,061 --> 00:34:10,301
Today I stand here

595
00:34:11,651 --> 00:34:13,381
to publicly apologize to someone.

596
00:34:16,821 --> 00:34:17,611
Wang Xiuyu.

597
00:34:20,701 --> 00:34:21,531
I'm sorry.

598
00:34:25,821 --> 00:34:26,931
Ten years ago,

599
00:34:28,221 --> 00:34:29,781
I went to university using your name.

600
00:34:30,301 --> 00:34:30,931
What?

601
00:34:31,891 --> 00:34:33,011
Went to university with another person's name?

602
00:34:34,411 --> 00:34:37,341
I had wondered why Xiuyu
didn't get into university

603
00:34:37,451 --> 00:34:38,571
with her good grades.

604
00:34:38,701 --> 00:34:39,451
Today,

605
00:34:40,141 --> 00:34:41,411
in front of everyone here,

606
00:34:42,741 --> 00:34:43,931
I wish to apologize formally to you.

607
00:34:49,931 --> 00:34:50,821
Xiuyu.

608
00:34:52,611 --> 00:34:53,491
I'm sorry.

609
00:35:09,301 --> 00:35:10,011
Xiuyu.

610
00:35:11,531 --> 00:35:12,971
You don't have to forgive me.

611
00:35:14,091 --> 00:35:14,821
I know

612
00:35:15,571 --> 00:35:17,221
my apology is years too late.

613
00:35:18,221 --> 00:35:18,891
But

614
00:35:19,341 --> 00:35:20,741
I finally understand now.

615
00:35:21,141 --> 00:35:23,011
No one can steal another person's life.

616
00:35:24,051 --> 00:35:26,141
And no one can live like how another person lives.

617
00:35:27,701 --> 00:35:29,091
We can only be ourselves.

618
00:36:20,051 --> 00:36:20,411
Hey.

619
00:36:20,741 --> 00:36:21,381
Mr. Wan.

620
00:36:21,531 --> 00:36:22,051
Xingfu.

621
00:36:22,051 --> 00:36:23,341
These are books for Chuanjia.

622
00:36:23,451 --> 00:36:24,381
Please pass them to him.

623
00:36:24,971 --> 00:36:26,411
Sorry for troubling you.

624
00:36:26,611 --> 00:36:27,971
Every time it's visiting day,

625
00:36:28,341 --> 00:36:29,261
you'd always remember.

626
00:36:29,381 --> 00:36:30,741
Thanks for your concern.

627
00:36:31,611 --> 00:36:32,971
Also, pass a message to him for me.

628
00:36:33,301 --> 00:36:35,221
Tell him to think of the prison term
as a learning period.

629
00:36:35,611 --> 00:36:36,781
Once he graduates and comes back,

630
00:36:36,891 --> 00:36:37,821
he can continue where he left off.

631
00:36:37,891 --> 00:36:38,661
Alright.

632
00:36:38,661 --> 00:36:40,051
Those are uplifting words.

633
00:36:40,571 --> 00:36:42,181
Sure, I'll pass on the message.

634
00:36:42,781 --> 00:36:43,491
He mentioned

635
00:36:43,701 --> 00:36:45,531
he's enjoying the books you brought for him.

636
00:36:46,301 --> 00:36:47,971
He said he did not

637
00:36:48,181 --> 00:36:48,971
like reading before.

638
00:36:49,341 --> 00:36:49,971
But now,

639
00:36:50,491 --> 00:36:52,341
once he starts, he can't stop.

640
00:36:53,261 --> 00:36:54,661
He said he must have had

641
00:36:55,341 --> 00:36:55,971
an enlightenment.

642
00:36:57,091 --> 00:36:58,781
His enlightenment sure came late.

643
00:36:58,781 --> 00:36:59,451
Indeed.

644
00:36:59,661 --> 00:37:01,491
The car is ready. Let's get going.

645
00:37:02,051 --> 00:37:02,661
Oh.

646
00:37:03,301 --> 00:37:04,661
Sorry for troubling you, Xingfu.

647
00:37:04,891 --> 00:37:05,571
Not at all.

648
00:37:06,261 --> 00:37:06,931
Xingfu.

649
00:37:07,301 --> 00:37:07,971
So,

650
00:37:08,181 --> 00:37:09,661
Chuanmei called.

651
00:37:09,661 --> 00:37:10,381
She said

652
00:37:10,661 --> 00:37:11,741
she wants to

653
00:37:11,781 --> 00:37:12,891
run a homestay

654
00:37:13,181 --> 00:37:14,181
at the place she teaches.

655
00:37:14,381 --> 00:37:15,051
But she has no experience.

656
00:37:15,381 --> 00:37:17,341
She's hoping you could go
and provide some guidance

657
00:37:17,341 --> 00:37:18,051
to give your thoughts.

658
00:37:18,051 --> 00:37:20,221
Sure. I'll call her later.

659
00:37:20,221 --> 00:37:20,661
Okay.

660
00:37:20,661 --> 00:37:22,261
How is she? Has she been well?

661
00:37:22,491 --> 00:37:23,341
Not too bad.

662
00:37:23,611 --> 00:37:24,571
The condition there is not too great.

663
00:37:24,861 --> 00:37:26,011
It's much tougher compared to here.

664
00:37:26,571 --> 00:37:28,301
But still, she's happy to be there.

665
00:37:29,261 --> 00:37:30,011
That's good.

666
00:37:30,741 --> 00:37:32,261
Xiuyu is doing well, I hope?

667
00:37:32,491 --> 00:37:34,891
Is she used to auditing classes
at the university?

668
00:37:35,301 --> 00:37:36,701
Yes, she is. She's also doing well.

669
00:37:37,261 --> 00:37:38,821
She said once she gets her bachelor's degree,

670
00:37:39,221 --> 00:37:40,701
she'll continue with postgraduate studies.

671
00:37:41,531 --> 00:37:42,221
Very ambitious.

672
00:37:43,091 --> 00:37:44,261
That's what "good days" are.

673
00:37:44,411 --> 00:37:45,611
They get brighter the farther you go.

674
00:37:48,244 --> 00:37:52,589
[Three years later]

675
00:37:52,589 --> 00:38:01,771
[Congratulations to Wan Village for winning
the title of "The Most Beautiful Highland Village"]

676
00:38:02,221 --> 00:38:02,821
Oh my.

677
00:38:03,011 --> 00:38:04,411
Look at this wide forehead.

678
00:38:04,861 --> 00:38:06,091
It's just like Xingfu.

679
00:38:07,341 --> 00:38:08,051
Ms. Lin.

680
00:38:08,611 --> 00:38:11,261
You two must already have your hands full
raising Little Dou.

681
00:38:11,531 --> 00:38:12,221
You should take a break.

682
00:38:12,221 --> 00:38:14,261
I can look after Little Juhua. Okay?
(*chrysanthemum)

683
00:38:14,491 --> 00:38:15,141
It's fine.

684
00:38:15,341 --> 00:38:16,261
You can rest.

685
00:38:16,821 --> 00:38:17,971
He's no trouble at all now that he's older.

686
00:38:19,381 --> 00:38:21,381
He and his little sister are inseparable.

687
00:38:21,661 --> 00:38:23,181
Whoever takes his sister away,

688
00:38:23,381 --> 00:38:25,261
he'll wreak havoc in the house.

689
00:38:25,861 --> 00:38:26,491
Ask him.

690
00:38:27,411 --> 00:38:28,181
Little Dou.

691
00:38:28,821 --> 00:38:31,531
Can I take Little Juhua away?

692
00:38:32,411 --> 00:38:33,051
No.

693
00:38:33,301 --> 00:38:33,741
No?

694
00:38:33,741 --> 00:38:35,181
She is my sister.

695
00:38:35,411 --> 00:38:36,451
I'll raise her.

696
00:38:37,531 --> 00:38:39,091
You're going to raise her?

697
00:38:39,531 --> 00:38:40,661
Okay, alright.

698
00:38:41,181 --> 00:38:43,221
I won't take your sister away.

699
00:38:44,531 --> 00:38:45,261
Tell your grandma.

700
00:38:45,661 --> 00:38:46,821
Next time,

701
00:38:46,821 --> 00:38:48,891
we'll bring Little Juhua to visit her often.

702
00:38:49,221 --> 00:38:49,571
Yes.

703
00:38:49,821 --> 00:38:50,411
Yes, that's right.

704
00:38:52,051 --> 00:38:52,531
Qinglai.

705
00:38:52,821 --> 00:38:54,931
How is your organic produce cooperative

706
00:38:54,931 --> 00:38:55,571
coming along?

707
00:38:55,861 --> 00:38:57,261
It's good. Very good.

708
00:38:57,451 --> 00:38:58,931
We're struggling to keep up with demands
from supermarkets.

709
00:38:59,141 --> 00:38:59,861
That's awesome.

710
00:39:00,221 --> 00:39:01,491
Qinglai, I saw Little Juhua just now.

711
00:39:01,491 --> 00:39:02,221
She's adorable.

712
00:39:02,341 --> 00:39:02,931
She is, isn't she?

713
00:39:04,221 --> 00:39:05,341
When will you two become parents?

714
00:39:05,491 --> 00:39:06,931
When can I become the elder uncle?

715
00:39:07,301 --> 00:39:08,971
Qingzhi, you better hurry up.
Know your priorities.

716
00:39:09,051 --> 00:39:10,181
Spend more time with Yani, you hear?

717
00:39:10,181 --> 00:39:10,971
Yes, I will.

718
00:39:20,011 --> 00:39:20,611
Qingzhi.

719
00:39:20,821 --> 00:39:21,411
Qinglai.

720
00:39:21,821 --> 00:39:23,091
-You're here, Mr. Guan.
-Mr. Guan.

721
00:39:23,491 --> 00:39:25,011
Guan Tao, Xingyun. What brings you here?

722
00:39:25,571 --> 00:39:26,451
We are organizing

723
00:39:26,611 --> 00:39:27,381
a monthly talk

724
00:39:27,611 --> 00:39:29,411
on law popularization with Wan Village.

725
00:39:29,531 --> 00:39:30,861
Today is the first session.

726
00:39:31,381 --> 00:39:31,781
Yes.

727
00:39:32,261 --> 00:39:33,141
I registered for it.

728
00:39:33,141 --> 00:39:34,451
I'm going to attend it in the afternoon.

729
00:39:35,611 --> 00:39:36,261
Mr. Wang.

730
00:39:36,971 --> 00:39:38,051
I've been wanting to talk to you.

731
00:39:38,821 --> 00:39:39,781
My cabbages

732
00:39:40,181 --> 00:39:40,891
have bugs.

733
00:39:41,381 --> 00:39:42,451
I don't know what to do.

734
00:39:43,141 --> 00:39:43,891
Don't fret.

735
00:39:44,051 --> 00:39:45,741
I'll go and take a look tomorrow.

736
00:39:46,141 --> 00:39:46,891
It's an easy fix.

737
00:39:47,571 --> 00:39:48,221
Excuse me.

738
00:39:48,491 --> 00:39:50,091
Everyone, please quiet down.

739
00:39:50,301 --> 00:39:52,451
Quiet down and get ready to start the meeting.

740
00:39:52,451 --> 00:39:53,861
Please gather around.

741
00:39:54,741 --> 00:39:56,571
Looks like we've got a big crowd today.

742
00:39:57,341 --> 00:39:58,781
Not just villagers of Wan Village,

743
00:39:59,011 --> 00:39:59,661
but also

744
00:40:00,141 --> 00:40:01,261
our friends, relatives,

745
00:40:01,261 --> 00:40:02,821
and people from neighboring villages.

746
00:40:03,931 --> 00:40:05,451
You must have heard about the good news.

747
00:40:06,091 --> 00:40:06,971
Firstly,

748
00:40:07,141 --> 00:40:09,091
we'll invite our county head, Mr. Liu,

749
00:40:09,781 --> 00:40:11,341
to give a speech.

750
00:40:11,411 --> 00:40:12,181
Put your hands together!

751
00:40:22,821 --> 00:40:24,611
Greetings, villagers of Wan Village.

752
00:40:25,411 --> 00:40:26,381
I am Liu Zhaofeng.

753
00:40:26,821 --> 00:40:27,861
Everyone must have heard.

754
00:40:28,451 --> 00:40:29,181
Recently,

755
00:40:29,661 --> 00:40:30,741
Wan Village

756
00:40:30,741 --> 00:40:32,781
was awarded a great honor.

757
00:40:33,301 --> 00:40:34,221
The honor

758
00:40:34,861 --> 00:40:36,091
was not only a testament

759
00:40:36,451 --> 00:40:37,301
to the success

760
00:40:37,661 --> 00:40:39,891
of Wan Village's efforts in alleviating poverty

761
00:40:40,301 --> 00:40:42,261
and creating a well-off society,

762
00:40:43,221 --> 00:40:44,091
it also meant

763
00:40:44,411 --> 00:40:45,451
that Wan Village

764
00:40:45,611 --> 00:40:48,571
managed to accrue good results

765
00:40:48,701 --> 00:40:51,531
in promoting cultural
and ideological progress

766
00:40:51,661 --> 00:40:53,491
and rule of law in the countryside.

767
00:40:59,141 --> 00:41:00,221
This honor

768
00:41:00,701 --> 00:41:01,611
didn't come easy.

769
00:41:02,221 --> 00:41:03,141
It took a lot of effort.

770
00:41:03,411 --> 00:41:06,051
You could say it was well-earned.

771
00:41:06,571 --> 00:41:09,381
It's not only an honor for Wan Village,

772
00:41:09,741 --> 00:41:11,611
but it's also an honor for the whole county.

773
00:41:11,931 --> 00:41:14,301
On behalf of the county party committee
and government,

774
00:41:14,781 --> 00:41:17,221
I'd like to congratulate Wan Village

775
00:41:17,221 --> 00:41:19,741
for receiving the national title
of "The Most Beautiful Highland Village".

776
00:41:20,301 --> 00:41:21,781
Wonderful!

777
00:41:23,221 --> 00:41:23,971
-Good.
-Good.

778
00:41:26,661 --> 00:41:28,411
I won't take up any more time.

779
00:41:28,931 --> 00:41:29,611
Now,

780
00:41:30,381 --> 00:41:31,011
I'd like to invite

781
00:41:31,221 --> 00:41:33,451
the new Wan Village party secretary on stage

782
00:41:33,451 --> 00:41:35,091
to say a few words.

783
00:41:35,381 --> 00:41:36,301
Let us welcome her.

784
00:41:36,661 --> 00:41:37,971
Good!

785
00:41:48,491 --> 00:41:49,181
Go on.

786
00:41:49,531 --> 00:41:49,971
Okay.

787
00:42:00,741 --> 00:42:01,491
Good day, everyone.

788
00:42:02,051 --> 00:42:03,011
I am He Xingfu.

789
00:42:05,451 --> 00:42:06,971
Congratulations to Wan Village

790
00:42:07,051 --> 00:42:09,341
for being awarded
"The Most Beautiful Highland Village".

791
00:42:10,571 --> 00:42:12,411
It wasn't easy to be given this honor.

792
00:42:13,301 --> 00:42:15,971
It's the result of the hard work

793
00:42:15,971 --> 00:42:18,181
from the cadres and people of Wan Village.

794
00:42:20,051 --> 00:42:21,451
But I wish to remind everyone

795
00:42:22,611 --> 00:42:24,491
that this honor only represented yesterday.

796
00:42:25,821 --> 00:42:27,741
Today, after this celebratory event,

797
00:42:28,571 --> 00:42:29,971
we have to put this honor aside

798
00:42:31,051 --> 00:42:33,341
and get ready to set out once more

799
00:42:33,341 --> 00:42:35,221
to reach new heights

800
00:42:35,221 --> 00:42:37,301
and create a better tomorrow!

801
00:42:37,301 --> 00:42:37,891
Yes?

802
00:42:37,971 --> 00:42:39,661
Yes!

803
00:42:42,141 --> 00:42:43,931
-Yes!
-Great!

804
00:43:27,671 --> 00:43:32,011
Maybe your life was broken

805
00:43:34,701 --> 00:43:38,571
Maybe you were rendered silent
by disappointment

806
00:43:40,691 --> 00:43:43,591
Even so, you need to move forward bravely

807
00:43:44,141 --> 00:43:46,971
And live as you persevere

808
00:43:47,541 --> 00:43:49,211
Who can stop you

809
00:43:49,671 --> 00:43:54,411
From living your best life?

810
00:43:54,841 --> 00:44:00,131
Maybe it has become even harder
to pursue your dream

811
00:44:01,461 --> 00:44:06,491
Maybe it's not all smooth sailing
throughout your life

812
00:44:08,221 --> 00:44:10,891
Even so, you need to move forward bravely

813
00:44:11,341 --> 00:44:14,211
And learn to be stronger

814
00:44:14,741 --> 00:44:16,411
Who can stop

815
00:44:17,061 --> 00:44:20,611
Happiness from blooming?

816
00:44:24,461 --> 00:44:27,531
Even if I will have my ups and downs

817
00:44:28,021 --> 00:44:30,091
I will never back down

818
00:44:30,621 --> 00:44:35,531
My crushed dreams are being reborn

819
00:44:36,781 --> 00:44:38,611
How could you know the broadness of the land

820
00:44:39,061 --> 00:44:42,491
Without climbing the tallest peaks

